47
00:04:50,340 --> 00:04:56,040
â™«   The wind becomes the monument for lovers   â™«

48
00:04:56,040 --> 00:05:01,620
If everything went back to where it began and the agarwood was reignited,

49
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:06,040
would you change your mind?

50
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:10,780
How many times do you want me to tell you?

51
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:14,520
For us to be together... It's impossible!

52
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:25,140
But you've looked back already, haven't you?

53
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:31,440
Yan Dan...

54
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:37,700
I'm willing to wait.

55
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:42,760
Waiting for you to come back to me again.

56
