57
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:54,300
As long as our hearts and our feelings are still there,

58
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:58,360
the lingering feeling will never disappear.

59
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:02,260
I'm the emperor.

60
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:04,160
I'm also Tang Zhou.

61
00:06:08,590 --> 00:06:13,970
When I complete my duty as emperor, Tang Zhou will come back

62
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:20,120
to spend the rest of his life with you.

63
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:36,760
Yan Dan,

64
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:41,380
wait for me.

65
00:07:35,770 --> 00:07:37,400
The letter from Tianxin Temple was burned.

66
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:40,260
But Ying Yuan is still investigating it and won't give up.

67
00:07:40,260 --> 00:07:42,620
Do you want me to intervene again?

68
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:59,520
There's no rush.

69
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:04,220
Even if he suspects now, it's already too late.

70
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:19,400
 It's already been five days. 

71
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:22,020
 Why hasn't Lu Ming come yet? 

72
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:26,960
Your Majesty!

73
00:08:30,140 --> 00:08:32,380
I was going to tell Lu Ming about Yan Dan.

74
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:36,240
But I've searched all over the Heavenly Realm the past few days, he is nowhere to be seen.

75
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:39,700
The immortal attendants of Yuqing Palace said it's been a long time since they last saw Lu Ming.

76
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:42,560
I felt something was wrong, so I rummaged through the Pavilion of Books.

77
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:46,980
All I found was the Merfolk Orb he left behind, but I don't know how to use it.

78
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:58,040
This is the magic weapon of the merfolk.

79
00:08:58,040 --> 00:09:00,340
Only merfolk can activate it.

80
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:14,520
Perhaps this will be helpful.

81
00:09:30,660 --> 00:09:32,500
What is this place?

82
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,680
The Merfolk are part of the Aquatic Clan of the North Sea.

83
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:38,300
This should be in the realm of the North Sea.

84
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:43,700
It must be a hint from Lu Ming. I have to go there and take a look.

85
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:56,400
You haven't recovered fully yet. You shouldn't work so hard.

86
00:09:56,400 --> 00:10:01,380
It's all right. Without Ground Block, the hot spring has lost its efficacy.

87
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:04,980
Now, I'm turning lotus spiritual power into a lotus to put it into the pool.

88
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:08,470
It makes it look nice and it can improve the efficacy of healing.

89
00:10:08,470 --> 00:10:12,370
So if the demons in the mountain are injured, they can keep bathing here and heal their wounds.

90
00:10:12,370 --> 00:10:14,780
It'll serve two purposes then, right?

91
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:17,780
You're such a responsible supporter.

92
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:20,560
Zi Lin should learn more from you.

93
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,720
Now all he does is stick to his wife.

94
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:25,280
He doesn't care about the mountain at all.

95
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,140
Elder, why have you come?

96
00:10:33,140 --> 00:10:35,600
His Highness, Lu Ming, has been missing for days now.

97
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,000
Did something happen to him?

98
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,960
His Highness works in the Heavenly Realm all year round.

99
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:41,840
He contacts us through the Merfolk Orb every day to handle the affairs of the North Sea.

100
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:44,700
For the past few days, we haven't received any messages from His Highness.

101
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:47,420
We could only cast a spell and activate the Merfolk Orb.

102
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:50,140
All we can see is this image.

103
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:56,560
This is the secret territory of the Merfolk known as Crystal Falls.

104
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,760
Since it is most sacred, there's a barrier.

105
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,420
No one from our clan can break it.

106
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:03,800
Even Her Majesty, the Dragon Queen, can't break through the barrier either.

107
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,460
We're anxiously looking for His Highness.

108
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:08,520
So Her Majesty told us to come to Yelan Mountain to ask for help.

109
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:09,820
Please don't worry, Elder.

110
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:14,020
I'll definitely try everything I can to figure out the truth and find Lu Ming.

111
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,960
Yan Dan.

112
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:31,320
 Yu Mo, I know that you want to go to the North Sea with me. 

113
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,180
 But the mountain just experienced a great disaster. 

114
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:36,300
 You should stay and guard the mountain so that the demons can feel at ease. 

115
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:38,500
 Don't worry. My cultivation base is enough now. 

116
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:42,620
 I'm sure I can use my power to protect myself and get Lu Ming back. 

117
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:44,080
 Please trust me. 

118
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,780
 Don't worry or miss me. 

119
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:48,500
 Wait for me, I'll return safely. 

120
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:50,180
Yu Mo.

121
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:55,260
Where is Yan Dan? Has she left already?

122
00:11:56,780 --> 00:12:01,680
Who was it that went missing that made the two of you so worried?

123
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:11,480
If you're worried, just go after her right now.

124
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,080
You can still catch up with her.

125
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:18,780
Since Yan Dan has made up her mind, I should respect her.

126
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:22,660
I believe that she'll get Lu Ming back.

127
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,820
Yan Dan.

128
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,980
Why are you here?

129
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,480
You came to the North Sea too.

130
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:02,400
You must've heard that Lu Ming went missing.

131
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:05,380
Are there any clues about him in the Heavenly Realm?

132
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:13,200
From Lu Ming's Merfolk Orb, I saw the waterscape of the North Sea.

133
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,200
So I followed the trace and came here.

134
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:30,920
Since we've run into each other, let's investigate it together.

135
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:33,060
 What matters is finding Lu Ming. 

136
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:34,360
 I don't know what the situation in the North Sea is like. 

137
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:37,200
 Another person means more help to be had. 

138
00:13:38,220 --> 00:13:40,080
All right, then.

139
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:50,400
According to the Elder, this should be Crystal Falls.

140
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:56,640
These are the Merfolk Tears that store memories.

141
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,700
We're too late.

142
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:02,120
I just used the Seven Immortal Powers to break this barrier.

143
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:06,680
The person who came before us must've been powerful.

144
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:10,920
Let's go check if that person left behind any leads.

145
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:19,360
There's a monument over here!

146
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:24,180
"Hundreds of generations of merfolk, numerous descendants."

147
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:28,020
"The Crystal Falls was formed to worship our ancestors."

148
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:30,980
"Life is short. We all return to the earth."

149
00:14:30,980 --> 00:14:34,120
"Year after year, you're remembered forever."

150
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:40,100
This is the ancestral hall of the Merfolk.

151
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:43,320
It is usually a place where they worship their ancestors.

152
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:47,340
If Lu Ming's Merfolk Orb is here, could it be...

153
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:50,300
It's impossible.

154
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:53,380
Lu Ming must have left me some more clues.

155
00:15:04,660 --> 00:15:06,620
How could this be?

156
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:09,900
Impossible.

157
00:15:16,100 --> 00:15:20,160
Yan Dan, Lu Ming gave us a hint to come here...

158
00:15:20,940 --> 00:15:22,680
Is he already...

159
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:24,360
Impossible.

160
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:26,280
Lu Ming isn't dead.

161
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:28,900
He must have been trying to leave me some clues.

162
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:31,080
I'm sure he's fine!

163
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:39,340
Yan Dan.

164
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:42,960
You can't activate the Merfolk Orb.

165
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,600
Stop trying.

166
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:55,480
Lu Ming must be waiting for me to rescue him.

167
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,260
He'll be fine.

168
00:15:57,260 --> 00:15:59,320
He'll definitely be all right.

169
00:16:13,860 --> 00:16:19,280
After one of the merfolk dies, a lifetime of memories will condense into a Merfolk Tear,

170
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:21,340
and fly back to the merfolk's homeland.

171
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:26,180
This is Lu Ming's Merfolk Tear.

172
00:16:27,620 --> 00:16:30,200
This is Spirit-Gathering Silk.

173
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,660
Lu Ming already had an ace up his sleeve.

174
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:35,420
Even though the person destroyed Lu Ming's Merfolk Tear.

175
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:41,240
But with Spirit-Gathering Silk, it can sense the breath of the host's kin.

176
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:46,220
It'll light up and it can somewhat gather his spirituality.

177
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:50,200
Lu Ming... what exactly have you been through?

178
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:53,220
What exactly happened to you?

179
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:04,640
 You wanted to see me, Your Supreme Majesty? 

180
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:11,700
 As an attendant, you should focus on your work and follow orders. 

181
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:16,120
 If you doubt your master, then that's the end of the road. 

182
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:23,260
How could it be His Supreme Majesty?

183
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:31,800
In the Three Realms, there are very few Immortals who can hurt you.

184
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:35,320
This mysterious man has always succeeded in sneaking up on you.

185
00:17:35,320 --> 00:17:38,900
He even tampered with the register and contacted the East Sea.

186
00:17:38,900 --> 00:17:43,420
It appears that His Supreme Majesty is indeed suspicious.

187
00:17:44,580 --> 00:17:47,240
His Supreme Majesty raised me.

188
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:49,800
He is my master and also my father.

189
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:52,780
How could he possibly try to kill me?

190
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:57,160
Besides, His Supreme Majesty isn't a hypocrite who does bad deeds.

191
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:59,560
He has ruled the Three Realms for millions of years.

192
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:04,100
The only thing he has done with an ulterior motive

193
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:08,440
was concealing the fact that I'm from the Asura bloodline.

194
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:12,520
There must be some hidden secret in all this.

195
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:18,220
Indeed, the mysterious man's act is totally incompatible with His Supreme Majesty's past behavior.

196
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:22,180
But Lu Ming took the risk to keep this scene.

197
00:18:22,180 --> 00:18:24,660
There must be something that he wanted to tell us.

198
00:18:26,620 --> 00:18:30,520
Perhaps... there are clues in the Merfolk Orb.

199
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:32,600
Let me take a look.

200
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:44,720
 Let's go, Lu Ming. 

201
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:47,480
 Wait. We haven't put the candles out yet. 

202
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:49,400
 Did you become crazy from working the night shift with me? 

203
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:51,000
 Let me help you put them out then. 

204
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,200
 Rest assured, Lu Ming. 

205
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:54,980
 Even if you're an immortal attendant in the Pavilion of Books for ten thousand years, 

206
00:18:54,980 --> 00:18:58,340
 I would do the night shift with you for ten thousand nights. Let's go! 

207
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:05,440
 How long is it going to take you doing it that way? Watch me. 

208
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:17,060
This was me and Lu Ming in the past.

209
00:19:23,340 --> 00:19:26,000
Lu Ming really is dead.

210
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:30,020
He and I had made a deal to accompany each other for ten thousand years.

211
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:35,920
But I went to the Mortal Realm and left him alone in the Nine Heavens.

212
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:40,540
I thought we would see each other again.

213
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:44,160
But now I'll never have a chance to see him again.

214
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:48,260
Lu Ming must be blaming me.

215
00:19:49,420 --> 00:19:52,140
He must be blaming me.

216
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:02,520
Lu Ming isn't blaming you.

217
00:20:03,860 --> 00:20:06,120
He was saying goodbye to you.

218
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:09,960
As for the two scenes that just appeared,

219
00:20:11,420 --> 00:20:15,600
he was trying to tell us that the location is at the Pavilion of Books.

220
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:19,320
Lu Ming must've prepared for this when he found some clues.

221
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:22,760
I'll go and check it out right now.

222
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:26,140
I'll come with you.

223
00:20:26,140 --> 00:20:31,440
If it's at the Pavilion of Books, I'm sure I can find the clues since I'm familiar with the place.

224
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:37,160
Yan Dan, you're a demon now.

225
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:39,200
If you get caught, your life would be in danger.

226
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:42,500
I'll be careful. Please believe me.

227
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:47,160
Lu Ming was murdered, but the culprit is still out there.

228
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:50,480
I can't just stay in the Mortal Realm and wait.

229
00:20:51,220 --> 00:20:54,060
Lu Ming was my best friend.

230
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,920
I want to avenge him.

231
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,760
I beg you.

232
00:21:01,180 --> 00:21:02,560
All right.

233
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:05,560
Let's go there together then.

234
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:15,300
   

235
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:27,620
Your Majesty.

236
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:29,880
There's no need to be so formal.

237
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:33,840
Today, I'd like to go through the ancient books in the Pavilion of Books.

238
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:35,560
I don't wish to be interrupted.

239
00:21:35,560 --> 00:21:37,180
Yes.

240
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:52,840
The Pavilion of Books appeared in Lu Ming's memory.

241
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:54,880
Let's split up and search.

242
