"I wish my friend, Yan Dan, peace and happiness."

246
00:22:58,260 --> 00:23:00,860
You prayed for me every year.

247
00:23:02,540 --> 00:23:06,600
But now, I can no longer give you my well wishes.

248
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:13,900
   

