00:23:13,900 --> 00:23:15,580
   

250
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:19,220
Why are there so many books about belts?

251
00:23:20,740 --> 00:23:23,260
 This was where I put the play scripts. 

252
00:23:23,260 --> 00:23:26,900
 Lu Ming never stored other books in here before. 

253
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:27,940
 What matters now is the investigation. 

254
00:23:27,940 --> 00:23:30,600
 I'll leave these personal effects aside for now. 

255
00:23:40,040 --> 00:23:42,000
Are there any clues?

256
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,680
I didn't find any.

257
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,600
Why don't we call it a day.

258
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:48,560
After a while, the patrolling immortal attendant will arrive.

259
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:50,300
Let's go.

260
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:51,980
Wait.

261
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:54,960
I meant to say...

262
00:23:54,960 --> 00:24:00,070
maybe the images Lu Ming left at the Crystal Falls weren't a farewell message to us.

263
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:12,240
As expected.

264
00:24:12,820 --> 00:24:16,940
Due to the special nature of the Merfolk's bone and blood, it can form an unquenchable fire.

265
00:24:16,940 --> 00:24:21,040
Lu Ming made these unquenchable candles with his own blood.

266
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:24,000
This is the clue that he wanted to show us!

267
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:46,280
Alignment of Nine Planets?

268
00:24:52,420 --> 00:24:56,880
The Alignment of Nine Planets is a very rare celestial phenomenon.

269
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,120
Yan Dan, look.

270
00:24:58,120 --> 00:25:00,220
The nine planets form an orderly line.

271
00:25:00,220 --> 00:25:04,520
They cover the sky and sun and form an array between heaven and earth.

272
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:07,540
I can't be as simple as a celestial phenomenon.

273
00:25:07,540 --> 00:25:09,820
When the Alignment of Nine Planets appears,

274
00:25:09,820 --> 00:25:12,520
if someone gathers the spiritual qi of heaven and earth with the Golden Cicada's Wings

275
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:18,140
and uses a powerful immortal spirit as the vessel to worship the Nine Planets Array,

276
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:20,760
they'll be able to achieve the Universe Enchantment.

277
00:25:24,980 --> 00:25:26,920
The Universe Enchantment?

278
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:33,920
The Universe Enchantment was used by the Lord of the Asura Clan, Xuan Ye.

279
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:38,660
Since it was sinister and vicious, it was banned after the War of Genesis.

280
00:25:38,660 --> 00:25:41,960
Only those elderly immortals who went through the War of Genesis know about it.

281
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:46,560
The Alignment of Nine Planets was last seen during the Divine-Devil War.

282
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:49,060
Use an immortal spirit as the vessel?

283
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:53,560
Immortal Lord Bei Ming's immortal spirit was lost after returning from the war.

284
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:58,400
Did someone do that on purpose to practice the Universe Enchantment with his immortal spirit?

285
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:03,560
But to achieve the Universe Enchantment needs the Golden Cicada's Wings.

286
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:06,380
It's the magic weapon of the Three-Winged Raven Clan.

287
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:08,040
That clan was annihilated long ago.

288
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:11,360
What will happen to those who are killed by the Universe Enchantment?

289
00:26:11,360 --> 00:26:14,600
The Universe Enchantment will engulf and absorb their divine power.

290
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:17,520
The immortal bones of those who are attacked will become brittle.

291
00:26:17,520 --> 00:26:18,940
It'll be hard for them to form a shape.

292
00:26:18,940 --> 00:26:21,740
Let's go to the Divine Cemetery Forest and check the body of Immortal Lord Bei Ming.

293
00:26:21,740 --> 00:26:24,020
Everything will come to light then.

294
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:28,920
Okay.

295
00:26:38,900 --> 00:26:44,120
Immortal Lord, you always said that you worked hard your whole life.

296
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:47,960
And if you ascended one day, you wished to eternally rest in the universe,

297
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,580
so that your existence could be peaceful.

298
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:56,260
But now, in order to give you justice, we must forcibly open your coffin and disturb your peace.

299
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:16,340
A GO piece!

300
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:28,920
 Your Majesty, long time no see. 

301
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:31,720
Immortal Lord?

302
00:27:35,060 --> 00:27:39,280
 A part of my spirituality rests on your GO piece. 

303
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:44,020
 Through it, I can connect with your heart and communicate telepathically with you. 

304
00:27:44,020 --> 00:27:45,880
My GO piece?

305
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:49,800
 In the Divine-Devil War, I was in charge of the rear 

306
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:54,180
  and allocated divine tools and immortal beasts to the immortals. 

307
00:27:54,180 --> 00:28:00,760
 On the eve of the war, His Supreme Majesty entrusted me to protect you if the war intensified. 

308
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:03,880
 However, I was at the rear and you were on the front line. 

309
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,920
 Worried that I wouldn't be able to take care of you, 

310
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:11,980
 I secretly took one of your GO pieces and connected it with your spiritual consciousness. 

311
00:28:11,980 --> 00:28:17,200
 After so many years, I didn't expect to meet you here. 

312
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:23,440
 If His Supreme Majesty really is that mysterious person, why would he save me and then try to kill me? 

313
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:31,420
Immortal Lord, I wasn't... aware of your kind intentions.

314
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:33,380
Now that the living and the dead are separated.

315
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:35,300
I can't repay you.

316
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:42,220
Can I ask, Immortal Lord, what happened exactly during the war that year?

317
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:53,640
 The Devils forced me into a hopeless situation. 

318
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:58,900
 I fought the devil soldiers up front, but one of them attacked from behind. 

319
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:03,440
 Caught off guard, I tried to see who it was. 

320
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:11,520
 I looked up... and saw my face. 

321
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:22,100
 I understood immediately that this person could use the Puppet Spell  

322
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:26,260
 to pretend to be someone else and hide his identity. 

323
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:36,600
 I couldn't expose him in the end. 

324
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:40,720
What happened that year was due to my oversight.

325
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:43,940
To prove your innocence to the Heavenly Realm,

326
00:29:43,940 --> 00:29:52,640
we have to ask your consent for us to open the coffin and find the evidence to avenge you.

327
00:29:52,640 --> 00:30:00,740
 This man plotted to kill celestial deities, absorb three emperors' divine power, and then quietly escape. 

328
00:30:00,740 --> 00:30:03,900
 He has fathomless immortal power and is very cunning. 

329
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:05,320
 Others are no match for him. 

330
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:09,440
 If you continue to pursue this, you'll put your life in danger. 

331
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:15,120
 Your identity will be exposed and staying in the Heavenly Realm will become difficult. 

332
00:30:15,120 --> 00:30:19,780
So, Immortal Lord, you already knew.

333
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:26,820
I dedicated my life to protecting the virtuous paths of the universe.

334
00:30:26,820 --> 00:30:29,940
I might expose my identity and lose my immortal status,

335
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:33,860
yet I need to seek justice for those who were innocent but implicated.

336
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:37,000
I'll perform my mission without fear and regret.

337
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:41,920
Immortal Lord, please allow us to open the coffin.

338
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,780
 All right. 

339
00:30:43,780 --> 00:30:46,680
 I knew it would end up like this. 

340
00:30:47,380 --> 00:30:49,880
 It was only a matter of time. 

341
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:56,280
 If you must get to the bottom of things and turn things around, you will face perils. 

342
00:30:56,940 --> 00:30:58,530
 If a war breaks out, 

343
00:30:58,530 --> 00:31:04,200
 I believe you'll definitely save all beings and restore peace to the Three Realms. 

344
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,800
 However, 

345
00:31:06,300 --> 00:31:08,400
 I have some selfish interests. 

346
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:13,380
Immortal Lord... are you concerned about Yan Dan and Yu Mo?

347
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:21,640
Don't worry. If they are dragged into this, I, Ying Yuan...

348
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:28,420
will bravely and selflessly protect them.

349
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:31,720
 Your Highness, I wish you safety and success. 

350
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:36,340
 I will entrust these two young ones to you then. 

351
00:31:41,720 --> 00:31:43,320
Immortal Lord.

352
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,780
Dragon scales?

353
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:58,360
Back then, Yu Mo put these dragon scales on his body.

354
00:31:58,360 --> 00:32:00,620
The Nine Fins Dragon Scales came from spiritual roots.

355
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:01,880
They're extremely hard.

356
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:05,600
Placed properly in a celestial coffin, they shouldn't break.

357
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:13,220
Sure enough, someone murdered celestial deities and took their immortal spirits to practice the Universe Enchantment.

358
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:20,020
In the Three Realms, there's only one who is capable of killing emperors.

359
00:32:21,060 --> 00:32:23,060
That's the Heavenly Emperor.

360
00:32:23,060 --> 00:32:28,640
In the War of Genesis, he led the immortals to destroy the Asura Clan.

361
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:33,200
Now, he uses Asura's evil art to harm those in the Heavenly Realm.

362
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:35,800
Why has he changed so much?

363
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:40,140
With his status, he used the Asura's evil art to harm those in the Heavenly Realm.

364
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:42,620
This is tantamount to subverting the Three Realms.

365
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:46,480
We must carefully confirm this.

366
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:51,600
If we want to find out the truth, we must collect more evidence.

367
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:58,100
I know that you have a deep friendship with him.

368
00:32:58,100 --> 00:33:02,980
If you investigate this, you'll be put in an extremely difficult situation.

369
