We can't let him take control of this.

372
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,560
Don't worry, Yan Dan.

373
00:33:10,560 --> 00:33:12,660
I won't be partial.

374
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,120
A lot is at stake.

375
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:20,220
I am duty-bound.

376
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:22,740
Before we have the evidence,

377
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:28,560
