378
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:35,240
Yan Dan. You should go back to Yelan Mountain first.

379
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,800
You're the emperor.

380
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:39,130
People will notice every move you make.

381
00:33:39,130 --> 00:33:44,430
If I pretend to be an immortal attendant, then I can move around more easily and undetected.

382
00:33:44,430 --> 00:33:48,560
Besides, Lu Ming left a wooden box in the Pavilion of Books.

383
00:33:48,560 --> 00:33:51,980
I have to figure out why he did that.

