00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:57,120
Since you've decided to stay,

385
00:33:58,500 --> 00:34:00,800
I will keep you safe.

386
00:34:10,180 --> 00:34:15,160
Immortal Lord, I will seek justice for you.

387
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:26,340
The Immortal Lord was Yu Mo's mentor.

388
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:30,580
The one who killed you in the mortal world also caused the extermination of the Nine Fins Clan.

389
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:35,060
Given Yu Mo's temperament, he will kill his enemy.

390
00:34:35,060 --> 00:34:39,240
I'll send him a letter to inform him about everything we've discovered.

391
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:44,020
After we get the evidence,

392
00:34:44,020 --> 00:34:48,740
